prompt.en:
Consider these two snippets for building a Map<String, List<Integer>>:
  A: map.getOrDefault(key, new ArrayList<>()).add(value);
  B: map.computeIfAbsent(key, k -> new ArrayList<>()).add(value);
Why does snippet A silently fail to accumulate values under an unseen key?

